<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Reliable Property Maintenance (R.P.M.)</title>

<style>
:root{
--red:#D62828;
--black:#000000;
--white:#FFFFFF;
--gray:#f4f4f4;
}

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#fff;
color:#000;
line-height:1.6;
}

header{
background:#000;
color:#fff;
padding:40px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

.logo{
width:180px;
height:180px;
border:10px solid white;
border-radius:50%;
margin:0 auto 20px;
position:relative;
}

.logo::before{
content:"";
position:absolute;
width:70px;
height:6px;
background:var(--red);
top:65px;
left:85px;
transform:rotate(-35deg);
transform-origin:left center;
}

.logo::after{
content:"RPM";
position:absolute;
bottom:30px;
left:50%;
transform:translateX(-50%);
font-size:30px;
font-weight:bold;
color:white;
}

h1{
font-size:3rem;
color:var(--red);
}

.tagline{
font-size:1.3rem;
margin-top:10px;
}

.btn{
display:inline-block;
background:var(--red);
color:white;
padding:15px 30px;
margin-top:20px;
text-decoration:none;
border-radius:8px;
font-weight:bold;
}

.section{
padding:60px 10%;
}

.section-title{
text-align:center;
color:var(--red);
margin-bottom:30px;
font-size:2rem;
}

.cards{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));
gap:20px;
}

.card{
background:white;
border:1px solid #ddd;
border-radius:10px;
padding:20px;
box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
}

.card h3{
color:var(--red);
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.card ul{
padding-left:20px;
}

.pricing{
background:var(--gray);
}

.booking{
background:#111;
color:white;
}

.booking form{
max-width:800px;
margin:auto;
display:grid;
gap:15px;
}

.booking input,
.booking select,
.booking textarea{
padding:12px;
border:none;
border-radius:6px;
}

.booking button{
background:var(--red);
color:white;
padding:15px;
border:none;
border-radius:6px;
cursor:pointer;
font-size:16px;
}

.loyalty{
background:#f8f8f8;
}

.footer{
background:black;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:30px;
}

.policy{
background:#fafafa;
}

.contact-box{
text-align:center;
font-size:18px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>

<div class="logo"></div>

<h1>Reliable Property Maintenance</h1>

<p class="tagline">
Your Property. Our Priority. Fast & Reliable.
</p>

#booking

</header>

<section class="section">
<h2 class="section-title">About R.P.M.</h2>

<p style="text-align:center;max-width:900px;margin:auto;">
Reliable Property Maintenance provides professional lawn care,
property maintenance, mini excavation, clean-outs, seasonal cleanups,
and snow removal throughout the Greater Rochester Area.
</p>
</section>

<section class="section">

<h2 class="section-title">Our Services</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<h3>🌱 Lawn Care & Maintenance</h3>
<ul>
<li>Weekly Lawn Mowing</li>
<li>Bi-Weekly Lawn Mowing</li>
<li>Vacation Lawn Care</li>
<li>Large Lot Mowing</li>
<li>Overgrown Grass Cutting</li>
</ul>
<br>
<strong>Residential:</strong> Set Pricing ($40-$60+)<br>
<strong>Commercial:</strong> Custom Estimates
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>✂️ Trimming & Edging</h3>
<ul>
<li>Weed Whacking</li>
<li>Fence Line Trimming</li>
<li>Driveway & Sidewalk Edging</li>
<li>Around Landscaping</li>
</ul>
<br>
<strong>Residential:</strong> $20-$50+<br>
<strong>Commercial:</strong> Custom Estimates
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>🌿 Brush & Overgrowth Removal</h3>
<ul>
<li>Property Line Clearing</li>
<li>Trail Maintenance</li>
<li>Field Edge Cleanup</li>
<li>Brush Removal</li>
<li>Shrub Removal</li>
</ul>
<br>
<strong>Residential:</strong> $75-$300+<br>
<strong>Commercial:</strong> Custom Estimates
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>🚜 Mini Excavation</h3>
<ul>
<li>Drainage Trenching</li>
<li>Utility Trenches</li>
<li>Post Hole Digging</li>
<li>Stump Removal</li>
<li>Grading & Leveling</li>
<li>Garden & Pond Excavation</li>
</ul>
<br>
<strong>Residential:</strong> $100/hr+<br>
<strong>Commercial:</strong> Project Estimates
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>🏠 House & Apartment Clean-Outs</h3>
<ul>
<li>Estate Clean-Outs</li>
<li>Foreclosure Clean-Outs</li>
<li>Rental Turnovers</li>
<li>Debris Removal</li>
</ul>
<br>
<strong>Residential:</strong> Set Pricing<br>
<strong>Commercial:</strong> Based on Number of Properties
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>🍂 Spring & Fall Cleanups</h3>
<ul>
<li>Leaf Cleanup</li>
<li>Storm Debris Removal</li>
<li>Fence Line Cleanup</li>
<li>Property Preparation</li>
</ul>
<br>
<strong>Residential:</strong> Set Pricing<br>
<strong>Commercial:</strong> Multi-Property Estimates
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>❄️ Snow Removal</h3>
<ul>
<li>Driveways</li>
<li>Small Commercial Lots</li>
<li>Sidewalk Clearing</li>
<li>Storm Cleanup</li>
</ul>
<br>
<strong>Residential:</strong> $30-$100+<br>
<strong>Commercial:</strong> Seasonal Contracts Available
</div>

</div>
</section>

<section class="section loyalty">

<h2 class="section-title">⭐ RPM Rewards</h2>

<div class="contact-box">
1 Point for every $10 spent<br>
10 Points for Reviews<br>
25 Points for Referrals<br><br>

25 Points = $10 Off<br>
50 Points = Free Trimming Service<br>
100 Points = $50 Credit
</div>

</section>

<section id="booking" class="section booking">

<h2 class="section-title">Book an Appointment</h2>

<form>

<input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" required>

<input type="tel" placeholder="Phone Number" required>

<input type="email" placeholder="Email Address">

<input type="text" placeholder="Property Address">

<select>
<option>Select Service</option>
<option>Lawn Maintenance</option>
<option>Brush Removal</option>
<option>Spring/Fall Cleanup</option>
<option>Mini Excavation</option>
<option>Snow Removal</option>
<option>House Clean-Out</option>
</select>

<input type="date">

<textarea rows="5" placeholder="Describe Your Project"></textarea>

<button type="submit">
Request Free Estimate
</button>

</form>

</section>

<section class="section policy">

<h2 class="section-title">Cancellation & Rescheduling Policy</h2>

<p>
✅ Reschedule within 12 hours of booking at no charge (if service is not within 24 hours).
</p>

<p>
✅ Lawn Care & Standard Services require 24-hour notice.
</p>

<p>
✅ Excavation Services require 48-hour notice.
</p>

<p>
✅ Weather-related delays are rescheduled free of charge.
</p>

<p>
✅ Weekly and bi-weekly customers may place services on hold with 48-hour notice.
</p>

</section>

<section class="section">

<h2 class="section-title">Contact Us</h2>

<div class="contact-box">
📍 Greater Rochester Area<br><br>

📞 (Insert Phone Number)<br>

📧 (Insert Email Address)<br><br>

FREE ESTIMATES
</div>

</section>

<footer class="footer">

<h2>R.P.M.</h2>

<p>Reliable Property Maintenance</p>

<p>Your Property. Our Priority. Fast & Reliable.</p>

<p>
Lawn Care • Property Maintenance • Mini Excavation • Snow Removal
</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
